{"id":"judgments-of-god","term":"Judgments of God","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>(1.) The secret decisions of God’s will (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 110:5\">Ps. 110:5</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 36:6\">36:6</a>). (2.) The revelations of his will (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 21:1\">Ex. 21:1</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Deuteronomy 6:20\">Deut. 6:20</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Psalms 119:7\">Ps. 119:7-175</a>). (3.) The infliction of punishment on the wicked (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 6:6\">Ex. 6:6</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 12:12\">12:12</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezekiel 25:11\">Ezek. 25:11</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Revelation 16:7\">Rev. 16:7</a>), such as is mentioned in <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 7:1\">Gen. 7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 19:24\">19:24</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 19:25\">25</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Judges 1:6\">Judg. 1:6</a>,<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Judges 1:7\">7</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Acts 5:1\">Acts 5:1-10</a>, etc.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Psalms 110:5","Psalms 36:6","Exodus 21:1","Deuteronomy 6:20","Psalms 119:7","Exodus 6:6","Exodus 12:12","Ezekiel 25:11","Revelation 16:7","Genesis 7:1","Genesis 19:24","Genesis 19:25","Judges 1:6","Judges 1:7","Acts 5:1"]}